  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1970770/extras/0938a597b50535ca1d94c106d105af79.avif?t=1728379700\" width=600 height=131 /></span><br><strong>''That's Gotta be the Best Pirate I've Ever Seen!''</strong><br>Purrate Adventure is a <strong>3D Platforming</strong> Cat Pirate Collect-A-Thon <strong>Adventure!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1970770/extras/84235e1a2dd6e0f7565fa871582a4061.poster.avif?t=1728379700\" width=600 height=116 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1970770/extras/84235e1a2dd6e0f7565fa871582a4061.webm?t=1728379700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1970770/extras/84235e1a2dd6e0f7565fa871582a4061.mp4?t=1728379700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Play as Mallow, the Cat Pirate! grabbing anything he can get his paws on.<br><br><strong>Explore & Plunder</strong> a large Volcanic Island in search of Coins, Gems, Crowns, and the 5 hidden Talismans!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1970770/extras/71f0c010c2f4057180c401bca269612e.poster.avif?t=1728379700\" width=600 height=116 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1970770/extras/71f0c010c2f4057180c401bca269612e.webm?t=1728379700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1970770/extras/71f0c010c2f4057180c401bca269612e.mp4?t=1728379700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Platform</strong> across the island using power-up combinations to cross a variety of obstacles!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1970770/extras/af48cd123b065b6fd4d7fe6d2956371c.poster.avif?t=1728379700\" width=600 height=116 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1970770/extras/af48cd123b065b6fd4d7fe6d2956371c.webm?t=1728379700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1970770/extras/af48cd123b065b6fd4d7fe6d2956371c.mp4?t=1728379700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Use a <strong>Dynamic Map & Camera Mode</strong> to navigate the non-linear Isle.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1970770/extras/f21faa22ded437f06f2dd758864c3b74.poster.avif?t=1728379700\" width=600 height=116 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1970770/extras/f21faa22ded437f06f2dd758864c3b74.webm?t=1728379700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1970770/extras/f21faa22ded437f06f2dd758864c3b74.mp4?t=1728379700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>15 Steam Achievements to Collect!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1970770/extras/159037069269eb5a920ea2d35a85ceaa.avif?t=1728379700\" width=600 height=116 /></span><br><br>Purrate Adventure: Volcano Isle is a project developed following player feedback closely. This has affected all the changes, fixes, and additions made to the game over the months leading to release.",
